{"tid":2458884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解人細個嘅時候會咁蠢....","createTime":"2021-03-23T19:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T03:32:52.000Z","uid":367538,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a413a290815d6bac3e27fb0769d676505a108fc1","tid":2458884,"uid":367538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:54:15.000Z","msg":"幼稚園嘅時候喺學校食lunch，嗰日有個紫菜魚蛋湯，但我咬唔爛啲紫菜，唔識吞但又唔想俾人見到我lur，就一直含咗成堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道一陣放學屋企人接我走嘅時候要同老師揮手講拜拜，驚到時一開口就被發現，我就一路上堂一路含住堆紫菜細聲練習講拜拜.........最後頂唔順話要去廁所然後lur咗落馬桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有就係我細個成日半夜瀨尿，又驚叫醒老母之後會俾佢鬧，所以我瀨完尿叫醒佢，就會問定佢：「如果我瀨尿你會唔會鬧我......」好似問咗就會安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebea12c7424d3ce133fc15c5027a715bc753320","tid":2458884,"uid":151454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"點解仲有記憶，我細個已經唔記得晒，淨係記得老竇帶我食麥當勞扭扭薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e92fe352faa813058e2fb2c9c5e2e3f31fc3b1b","tid":2458884,"uid":367538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ebea12c7424d3ce133fc15c5027a715bc753320","tid":2458884,"uid":151454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"點解仲有記憶，我細個已經唔記得晒，淨係記得老竇帶我食麥當勞扭扭薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:58:01.000Z","msg":"因為太驚心動魄，到而家仲記得當時幾緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7f5f99eed8f1728d9b42a63d1bd5212478c2f9","tid":2458884,"uid":383344,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T20:07:48.000Z","msg":"小一無啦啦有條友想扯甩我條褲 話想知我有無底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔搵你自己個條，我真誠地問。之後一堆人追住去扯佢條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52bd7b7a1f40567b086a52e7e06a294f3dc0638","tid":2458884,"uid"